026-03-20 — Run 61\n\n**Status:** All clear\n\n**Checked:**\n- Tests: social-tools (136✓), groceryGenius (81✓), pezantTools (51✓), runeval (53✓), promptlibrary (66✓), activity-tracker (44✓), job-scraper (59✓), valueSortify (38✓), waymo-sim (34✓) — 562 total, all passing\n- Builds: all 8 repos with build scripts pass cleanly\n- PM2: all 11 processes online; staging services healthy (runeval-staging 2, promptlibrary-staging 1, grocerygenius-staging 2 restarts)\n- Git status: cleaned up stale claude/auto-sort-pagination (local) and pruned stale remote tracking refs for claude/auto-sort-pagination and claude/auto-share-links in social-tools (already deleted on GitHub by PR merge)\n- Open PRs: none across all 15 repos\n- Autonomous dev logs: runs 34-37 completed cleanly, no FAIL entries\n\n**Fixed:** Cleaned up stale agent branches in social-tools (local `claude/auto-sort-pagination` deleted, pruned 2 stale remote tracking refs). No broken builds/tests/services.","originalFile":"# Fix Checker Failure Log\n\nEach entry is appended by the fix-checker agent after every run.\nThis log helps identify recurring issues and track what's been checked.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-19 — Run 1\n\n### Checked\n- **All repos**: builds, tests, git status, open PRs\n- **PM2**: all processes online (no issues)\n- **Test results**: groceryGenius (81 pass), pezantTools (51 pass), runeval (53 pass), promptlibrary (66 pass), valueSortify (38 pass), job-scraper (59 pass), activity-tracker (44 pass), social-tools (28 pass), llm-tasks (151 pass), waymo-sim (32 pass after fix)\n- **Builds**: groceryGenius, pezantTools, runeval — all passing\n- **Open PRs**: none across all repos\n\n### Fixed\n- **waymo-sim**: Invalid `build-backend` in `pyproject.toml` — was `setuptools.backends._legacy:_Backend` (nonexistent), changed to `setuptools.build_meta`. This prevented `pip install` and blocked all 32 tests from running. PR #10, auto-merged.\n\n### Notes\n- Git push via HTTPS still silently fails on some repos;