ls 11, claude-auto-merger 6, runeval 6, grocerygenius 5, activity-tracker 2, runeval-staging 2, grocerygenius-staging 2, promptlibrary 1, promptlibrary-staging 1, pm2-logrotate 0)\n- **Uncommitted work**: llm-tasks has 7 files (daily job pipeline output, not agent work — no action needed)\n- **Autonomous dev logs**: no new failures\n\n### Fixed\n- Nothing — all clear.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-19 — Run 4\n\n### Checked\n- **All repos tests**: groceryGenius (81 pass), pezantTools (51 pass), promptlibrary (66 pass), runeval (53 pass), valueSortify (38 pass), job-scraper (59 pass), activity-tracker (44 pass), social-tools (28 pass), llm-tasks (151 pass)\n- **waymo-sim**: tests fail locally (missing `gymnasium` dep in local env) but CI passes — not broken\n- **Open PRs**: none across all 15 repos\n- **PM2**: all 11 processes online, restart counts stable\n- **Uncommitted work**: llm-tasks has daily job pipeline output (expected, not agent work)\n- **Stale branches**: pezantTools and social-tools have old claude/* remote branches — housekeeping only\n\n### Fixed\n- Nothing — all clear.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 5\n\n### Checked\n- **All repos tests**: groceryGenius (81 pass), pezantTools (51 pass), promptlibrary (66 pass), runeval (53 pass), valueSortify (38 pass), job-scraper (59 pass), activity-tracker (44 pass), social-tools (28 pass), llm-tasks (151 pass)\n- **waymo-sim**: tests fail locally (missing venv) but CI passes — not broken\n- **Open PRs**: none across all repos\n- **PM2**: all staging processes online, restart counts normal\n- **Uncommitted work**: valueSortify on `claude/auto-design-system` branch with 8+ uncommitted files (crashed agent); llm-tasks has daily pipeline output (expected)\n- **Autonomous dev logs**: no failures\n\n### Fixed\n- **valueSortify**: Recovered crashed agent session — design system changes across 8 files were complete (build + 38 tests passing). Committed and pushed as PR #14 (auto-merged). Found 3 additional components (DraggableCar